   <pb facs="135"/>
   <head>To the Reader.</head>
   <p>
      <hi>¶ Pardon (discreet reader) to many errors escaped in the prin<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>ting because they hardly could be auoyded: the Author beeing absent, the Printer being ignorant of our language, the stile not vulgar and the Copy not very persect. Yet I thought good with all these impediments not to depriue thee of so necessa<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>ry a medicine, howbeit the glasse being something brused.</hi>
   </p>
